commitResults.messageBody: Fix model equal function to not contain associations

Property preference has an association with an old version of the tag
given bidirectional navigability and immutability requiring recreation
of tags. Deleting a property preferences updates the tag with the old
tag which does not contain the associations to property preferences,
thus outputting 0 as the tag counter when a property preference is
deleted.

Use mutable associations to simplify the code for ease of readability
and maintenance
